  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">
    API testing and request workflows for developers
  </p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    PingPong is a lightweight browser extension for API testing, built as a practical alternative to heavy API clients. 
    It brings request workflows directly into your browser.
  </p>

  <h2>Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Send HTTP requests from your browser</li>
    <li>Manage request collections</li>
    <li>Environment variables and custom headers</li>
    <li>Request history tracking</li>
    <li>Lightweight and fast</li>
  </ul>

